  "learningOutcomes": [
    "LO1: Distinguish between alcohols and phenols based on the hybridization of the carbon atom bonded to the hydroxyl group.",
    "LO2: Apply IUPAC nomenclature rules to name mono-hydric alcohols and simple phenols correctly.",
    "LO3: Classify given alcohol structures as primary, secondary, or tertiary."
