        "Distribute cards with chemical structures of various alcohols and phenols (e.g., Ethanol, Phenol, Propan-2-ol, Benzyl alcohol).",
        "Students work in pairs to sort them into two piles: 'Alcohol' vs 'Phenol'.",
        "For the Alcohol pile, students must further classify each as Primary, Secondary, or Tertiary.",
        "Teacher circulates and checks reasoning (e.g., asking why Benzyl alcohol is an alcohol despite having a ring)."
      ],
      "durationMinutes": 10
    }
  ],
